data.description: Welcome to your ideal family haven, conveniently situated for an effortless commute to Ft. Liberty. This remarkable 3 bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence, complete with a spacious 3-car garage, sits on a generous corner lot .A charming covered front porch sets the tone for a warm welcome. Step inside to discover the well-designed main level, featuring a versatile den/office space, perfect for remote work or quiet study. The formal dining room provides an elegant setting for special occasions, while the large family room, complete with a fireplace, is a great spot to unwind.The heart of this home lies in its kitchen, where the perfect blend of style & functionality comes to life. With granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & an inviting island with a breakfast bar, this kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream. A walk-in pantry ensures ample storage, & the adjacent breakfast room offers a sunlit space for casual dining or morning coffee.Upstairs, the 3 generously sized bedrooms provide comfortable retreats for the whole family. The master suite, a true sanctuary, boasts a well-appointed ensuite bathroom & his and hers walk-in closets, separate sinks, shower & tub creating a private haven to relax after a long day. There is also a huge bonus room and a flex room upstairs to be utilized to suit your lifestyle.Outside, the property unfolds into a sprawling oasis, perfect for outdoor gatherings & play. The sizable corner lot provides flexibility for landscaping and recreation, offering endless possibilities for your family's enjoyment.With its prime location, ample living space, and thoughtful design, this home not only meets but exceeds the needs of a modern family. Don't miss the chance to make this residence your own, where every detail has been carefully crafted to enhance the comfort & convenience of your daily life. Schedule your viewing today & envision the possibilities that await you in this fantastic family home.
